title: The AutoPlay dialog box does not appear when connect E5377Bs-605 to PC with USB cable
answer:
A: 

 1. Please check if the computer OS meets one of the following:  

 (1)     Windows XP(32 bit) / Windows Vista / Windows 7/ Windows 8 

 (2)     MAC OS X 10.5, MAC OS X 10.6, MAC OS X 10.7/MAC OS X 10.8 

 2. Make sure E5377Bs-605 is turned on (OLED screen has lighten up and have WiFi icon has displayed information as Q4). To turn on E5377Bs-605, hold and press “Power Key![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=39321)” for 3 second. If E5377Bs-605 is out of battery power, please charge it by USB cable or power adaptor.
